{
  "stem": "5188.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the teacher said to me, as a greeting, hello.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Oh, I see your sister is here, and I hope you'll be as good as your sister.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And from that moment I was determined not to be as good as my sister.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I was going to be my own self.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I must say, even though I always passed everything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I have my old report cards.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It-- it always said gut, gut, gut, but it never said sehr gut, except maybe for behavior or something like that.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But somehow, I never got those sehr guts.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I really didn't try very hard.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Because who wanted to be so good like my sister who always gets sehr good in everything-- sehr gut meaning, very good, of course.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was my introduction to school in Germany.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But by and large, the teacher, whose name was Mrs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Klumper, Frau Klumper-- and that's spelled K-L-U with an umlaut-- M-P-E-R-- was really a nice, motherly kind of person.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember her being big and a bit stout.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she treated me all right.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- she certainly was no Nazi, considering that I started school in 1933.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she was, I think, my teacher for the first three or four grades.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't remember exactly when it changed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then, I know in my very last year in school, in Germany, which was in the fifth grade, I had another teacher, a man, a Herr Mohr, M-O-H-R.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he-- he was really very nice, really-- also a wonderful person.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I-- I didn't suffer from my teachers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The school itself was actually a Catholic school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was what we call a public school and a volksschule, but it was the Katholische volksschule, which means it was a Catholic public school.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
